{"tid":249463,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"恒生指數有限公司宣佈指數檢討結果","createTime":"2017-05-19T10:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T12:26:16.000Z","uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"729b4a2bc7f4bbd2343acb6373eddcf0c7656ffe","tid":249463,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:13:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hsi.com.hk/HSI-Net/static/revamp/contents/zh_hk/news/pressRelease/20170519c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsi.com.hk%2FHSI-Net%2Fstatic%2Frevamp%2Fcontents%2Fzh_hk%2Fnews%2FpressRelease%2F20170519c.pdf&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVphOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e23deea2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hsi.com.hk/HSI-Net/static/revamp/contents/zh_hk/news/pressRelease/20170519c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"8e8796339577876ec98b87502e3152de950635eb","tid":249463,"uid":107720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"700 騰訊控股 60 11.78 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 10.00<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb7e645459a754b1eac904fc61c52b7ca3a7959","tid":249463,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>700 騰訊控股 60 11.78 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 10.00<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n** 比重變動反映滙豐控股和騰訊控股之比重被調整至10%上限及流通系數之變動。"},{"pid":"e0612377add8e8561a8fba5fa545a5578f48b442","tid":249463,"uid":42420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:06:59.000Z","msg":"咁個市會點?其他升番700 d 比重?"},{"pid":"88fd197ccdb3d06571a30be28bed86636b7ff9df","tid":249463,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁個市會點?其他升番700 d 比重?</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56716528&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56716528%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVphOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=481710e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56716528%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&h=e57e90f4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56716528&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519</a><br />\n恒生指數有限公司宣佈今年首季恒生指數系列季度檢討結果,恒生指數成份股沒有變動，成份股數目固定為50隻;恒生中國企業指數成份股亦沒有變動，成份股數目固定為40隻。<br />\n<br />\n恒生指數公司表示，根據諮詢的市場人士意見，決定將<span style=\"color: red;\">紅籌股及民營企業加入恒生中國企業指數</span>,同時將根據公司的業務覆蓋範圍以界定民營企業。恒生指數公司現正研究其他關於實施方式的詳情,包括：一)加入紅籌股及民營企業的合適數目;二)挑選紅籌股及民營企業的合適準則;及三)如何實施變動以減低可能對市場的潛在影響。<br />\n<br />\n恒生指數公司預計將於2017年8月公佈詳情。<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經生活資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVphOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=69bc96a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\n桌面版使用說明使用條款聯絡我們<br />\n&copy;2017 AD Internet Limited.<br />\nAll rights reserved. 版權所有 不得轉載"},{"pid":"7ace26d999f30491d64c49f5fc6a818c7dca3322","tid":249463,"uid":58228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T12:26:16.000Z","msg":"減左QQ比重 變相推恆指上落影響細d"}]}